  m_text: "Burve ir slepena, m\u0101c\u012Bga pasaules sarg\u0101t\u0101ja, kas apvieno
    zino\u0161u pr\u0101tu ar sirsn\u012Bgu r\u016Bpi pret citiem. Vi\u0146as valod\u0101
    main\u0101s v\u0113ja v\u0113sti, bet smieklos dzirdami senos nosl\u0113pumu
    atbalsis. Burve prot izmantot gan senus burvest\u012Bbu z\u012Bm\u0113jumus,
    gan m\u016Bsdien\u012Bgu gudr\u012Bbu, lai vad\u012Btu citus uz dro\u0161\u0101m,
    bet aizraujo\u0161\u0101m izv\u0113l\u0113m sav\u0101 ce\u013C\u0101. Vi\u0146as
    t\u0113la ap\u0123\u0113rbs ir daudzsl\u0101\u0146ains, pilns ar z\u012Bm\u0113m
    un simboliem, kas atspogu\u013Co gan iek\u0161\u0113jo, gan \u0101r\u0113jo pasauli."
